Revision history for Perl extension FileDirUtil.

0.01  Sun May 14 2017
	- initial release

0.02  Tue May 23 2017
	- provide set_ifilebn() method

0.03  Sun May 28 2017
	- $self->odir now accepts a Path::Class::Dir object or an ArrayRef
          of path segments that will be coerced into a Path::Class::Dir
          object
